quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  11,41,"“Ndipo (Nuh) adati: “Kwerani m’menemo mwadzina la Allah mkuyenda kwake ndi mkukocheza kwake. Ndithu Mbuye wanga Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni zedi.”"
  11,42,"“Ndipo (chombocho) chidali kuyenda nawo m’mafunde onga mapiri, ndipo Nuh adaitana mwana wake yemwe adali patali (atakana kulowa m’chombo): “Mwana wanga! Kwera pamodzi ndi ife usakhale pamodzi ndi osakhulupirira.”"
  11,43,"“(Iye) adati: “Ndithawira kuphiri likanditeteza ku madziwa.” Nuh adati: “Lero palibe otetezedwa ku lamulo la Allah kupatula yemwe Allah wamchitira chifundo.” Pompo mafunde adatchinga pakati pawo. Choncho adali mgulu la omizidwa"
  11,44,"“Ndipo (pambuyo poonongeka onse ndi zonse zomwe Allah adafuna kuti zionongeke), kudanenedwa: “E iwe nthaka! Meza madzi ako. Ndipo iwe thambo! Amange (madzi ako amvula).” Choncho, madzi adaphwa ndipo lamulo lidakwaniritsidwa (loononga anthu oipa). Ndipo (chombo) chidaima pamwamba pa (phiri lotchedwa) Judi, ndipo kudanenedwa: “Aonongeke onse ochita zoipa.”"
  11,45,"“Ndipo Nuh adafuulira Mbuye wake nati. “E Mbuye wanga! Ndithu mwana wanga ali mgulu la akubanja langa (akuonongedwa). Ndipo ndithu lonjezo lanu ndiloona, ndipo Inu Ndinu Woweruza mwachoonadi kuposa aweruzi onse.”"
  11,46,"“(Allah) adati: “E iwe Nuh! Ndithu iyeyo si (mwana) wa m’banja lako. Iye zochita zake sizili zabwino. Choncho usandipemphe zomwe siukuzidziwa, Ine ndikukulangiza kuti usakhale m’gulu la osazindikira (mbuli).”"
  11,47,"“(Nuh) adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndikudziteteza mwa Inu kuti ndisakupempheninso zomwe sindikuzidziwa. Ngati simundikhululukira ndi kundichitira chifundo, ndikhala mwa anthu otaika.”"
  11,48,"“Kudanenedwa: “E iwe Nuh! Tsika (pa nthaka youma) mwamtendere wochokera kwa Ife, ndipo madalitso ambiri akhale pa iwe ndi pa anthu omwe ali nawe; ndipo kudzakhala mibadwo ina (yoipa pambuyo pako) yomwe tidzaisangalatsa, ndipo kenako chidzaikhudza chilango chowawa chochokera kwa Ife.”"
  11,49,"“Izi ndi zina mwa nkhani zobisika zomwe tikukuululira iwe. Siudali kuzidziwa, iwe ngakhale anthu ako, patsogolo pa ichi, (Qur’an isadadze). Choncho, pirira. Ndithu mathero abwino adzakhala kwa anthu oopa Allah"
  11,50,"“Ndipo anthu (amtundu) wa Âdi, tidawatumizira m’bale wawo Hûd. Adati: “E inu anthu anga! Pembedzani Allah! (Siyani kupembedza mafano). Mulibe mulungu wina koma Iye. Inu simuli kanthu koma ndinu opeka bodza (m’kunena kwanu kwakuti mafano ndi anzake a Allah).”"
  11,51,““E inu anthu anga! Sindikukupemphani malipiro pa ichi (uthengawu). Palibe Malipiro anga koma ali kwaYemwe adandilenga. Kodi mulibe nzeru?”
  11,52,"““Ndipo E inu anthu anga! Pemphani chikhululuko kwa Mbuye wanu, (pa machimo omwe mwakhala mukuchita), kenako lapani kwa Iye. Akutumizirani mitambo yodzetsa mvula yambiri, ndipo akuonjezerani mphamvu pa mphamvu zanu (zomwe muli nazo). Choncho, musatembenuke kukhala oipa.”"
  11,53,"“(Iwo) adati: “E iwe Hûd! Sudatibweretsere chisonyezo chooneka (chosonyeza kuti ndiwe Mneneri), ndipo ife sitisiya (kupembedza) milungu yathu chifukwa cha zoyankhula zakozo. Ndipo ife sitikukhulupirira.”"
  11,54,"““Sitinena kanthu, koma kuti (mwina) milungu yathu ina yakulodza misala.” (Iye) adati: “Ndithu ine ndikupereka umboni kwa Allah ndipo inunso perekani umboni kuti ine ndili kutali ndi zimene mukumphatikiza nazo (Allah pomazipembedza).”"
  11,55,"““Kusiya Iye; (milungu yanuyo sindikuiopa ngati ili ndi mphamvu pamodzi ndi inu), tero ndichitireni chiwembu nonsenu, ndipo kenako musandiyembekezere (musandipatse nthawi).”"
  11,56,"““Ndithu ine ndatsamira kwa Allah, Mbuye wanga yemwenso ali Mbuye wanu. Palibe chinyama chilichonse koma Allah wachigwira tsumba lake (ndikuchiyendetsa mmene akufunira). Ndithudi, Mbuye wanga Ngwachilungamo.”"
  11,57,"““Ngati munyoza (kulandira chimene ndakuuzani palibe vuto kwa ine); ndithu ndafikitsa kwa inu chimene ndatumidwa. Ndipo Mbuye wanga (awaononga osakhulupirira, ndipo) abweretsa anthu ena m’malo mwanu, ndipo inu simungamusautse konse. Ndithu Mbuye wanga ndi Msungi wa chilichonse.”"
  11,58,"“Ndipo pamene lamulo lathu lidafika (lakuwaononga), tidampulumutsa Hûd ndi amene adakhulupirira pamodzi naye, mwachifundo Chathu, ndipo tidawapulumutsa kuchilango chokhwima"
  11,59,"“Ndipo awa ndi Âdi. Adatsutsa Ayah (ndime) za Mbuye wawo ndi kunyoza atumiki Ake; ndipo adatsata lamulo la yense wodzikweza, wamakani"
  11,60,"“Ndipo adatsatizidwa ndi tembelero pa moyo wapano padziko lapansi ndi tsiku la Qiyâma (tsiku la chiweruziro). Dziwani! Ndithu Âdi adakana Mbuye wawo. Ha! Adaonongeka Âdi, anthu a Hûd"